amarantin command reference
===========================

Enter the GPVM container environment
    source ./.container.sh

Set up the GPVM software environment
    source ./.setup.sh

Configure the build
    cmake -S . -B build -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release

Build the project
    cmake --build build --parallel

Generate all sample lists from datasets.mk
    make -f samples-dag.mk samples-lists

Build all sample ROOT files from datasets.mk
    make -f samples-dag.mk samples

Print all managed sample ROOT targets
    make -f samples-dag.mk print-samples

Remove generated sample ROOT files and sample lists
    make -f samples-dag.mk samples-clean

Generate one sample list directly
    tools/mklist.sh --dir /path/to/input --pat "nu_selection.root,nu_selection_data.root" --out samplelists/example.list

Build one sample ROOT file directly
    build/bin/mk_sample output.root input.list data nominal numi fhc
